<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Equilibrium: 方程平衡之旅</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        .bracket-bubble { animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); border-color: rgba(147, 51, 234, 0.5); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.02); border-color: rgba(147, 51, 234, 1); }
        }
        .term-node { transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <header class="bg-slate-800 border-b border-slate-700 p-4 sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-md">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="bg-indigo-600 p-2 rounded-lg text-white">⚖️</div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Equilibrium</h1>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">自主试错型方程五维熟练度系统</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-4 text-xs">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-emerald-950 text-emerald-400 rounded border border-emerald-800">🧩 概念理解 (CU)</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-950 text-blue-400 rounded border border-blue-800">⚡ 程序熟练度 (PU)</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-amber-950 text-amber-400 rounded border border-amber-800">🎯 策略能力 (SC)</span>
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-purple-950 text-purple-400 rounded border border-purple-800">🧠 渐进推理 (AR)</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-1 max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto p-4 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        
        <aside class="lg:col-span-1 bg-slate-800/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 h-fit">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4"><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group mr-2"></i> 核心课程关卡</h2>
            <div class="space-y-2" id="level-list"></div>
            <button onclick="resetCurrentLevel()" class="w-full mt-4 p-2 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 rounded text-xs font-bold text-rose-400 border border-rose-900/50 cursor-pointer transition">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-rotate-left mr-1"></i> 重置当前方程状态
            </button>
        </aside>

        <section class="lg:col-span-2 flex flex-col space-y-4">
            
            <div class="bg-indigo-950/40 border border-indigo-900/60 p-4 rounded-xl flex flex-col space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                    <span class="text-xl">🚀</span>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-indigo-300" id="quest-title">正在加载...</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 mt-1" id="quest-desc">加载中...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div id="modeling-zone" class="bg-slate-900/60 p-3 rounded-lg border border-indigo-800/60 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3">
                    <div class="text-xs text-indigo-200 font-medium">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-pen-ruler mr-1"></i> 请将上方情境转化为初始代数方程：
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex w-full sm:w-auto items-center space-x-2">
                        <input type="text" id="equation-input" placeholder="例如: x + 3 = 8" class="flex-1 sm:w-44 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm bg-slate-800 border border-slate-600 rounded text-slate-100 placeholder-slate-500 font-mono text-center">
                        <button onclick="verifyModelingFormula()" class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 rounded text-xs font-bold text-white shadow cursor-pointer">提交</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="core-interactive-container" class="space-y-4 relative opacity-30 pointer-events-none transition-all duration-500">
                
                <div id="lock-overlay" class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/10 z-40 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-indigo-400">
                    <span class="bg-slate-950/90 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-xs">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-lock mr-2 text-amber-500 animate-pulse"></i>请先建立方程建模以解锁天平
                    </span>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-inner relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[160px]">
                    <div class="absolute top-2 left-3 text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono">🧩 真实重力天平 (永远保持水平平衡，仅展现内部物块质变)</div>
                    
                    <div class="w-full max-w-sm flex flex-col items-center mt-2">
                        <div class="w-full flex justify-between items-end px-4" id="balance-beam">
                            <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1 w-5/12 bg-slate-700/30 p-2 rounded-t-lg border-b-4 border-indigo-500 text-center">
                                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 justify-center min-h-[40px] items-center" id="left-pan-visual"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-1.5 h-14 bg-slate-600 self-center"></div>
                            <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-1 w-5/12 bg-slate-700/30 p-2 rounded-t-lg border-b-4 border-emerald-500 text-center">
                                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 justify-center min-h-[40px] items-center" id="right-pan-visual"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-20 h-2 bg-slate-600 rounded-full"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-6 relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[140px]">
                    <div class="absolute top-2 left-3 text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono">⚡ 当前代数表达式状态 (无现成答案显示，支持完全自主演算)</div>
                    
                    <div class="text-xl font-bold tracking-wide my-4 flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-1.5 text-center" id="algebraic-display"></div>

                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mt-2">
                        <span id="status-indicator" class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                        <div id="operation-feedback" class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-300 italic">请先点击上面的项，然后对其施加逆运算</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="toolbox" class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/60 rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col space-y-3 opacity-40 pointer-events-none transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-bold flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span>🛠️ 选择你想对选中的项执行的代数变形操作：</span>
                        <span id="selected-target-badge" class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-indigo-950 text-indigo-400 rounded border border-indigo-800 hidden">未选中项</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 items-center bg-slate-900/40 p-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-700">
                        <div class="text-xs text-slate-300 font-medium pl-1">对两边同时输入常数/系数：</div>
                        <input type="text" id="operation-value" placeholder="输入数字，如: 3 或 -2" class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-600 rounded font-mono text-center text-slate-100">
                        <div class="flex space-x-1">
                            <button onclick="executeAction('add_sub')" class="flex-1 py-1 bg-indigo-700 hover:bg-indigo-600 text-xs font-bold rounded cursor-pointer transition">执行 加/减</button>
                            <button onclick="executeAction('mul_div')" class="flex-1 py-1 bg-indigo-700 hover:bg-indigo-600 text-xs font-bold rounded cursor-pointer transition">执行 乘/除</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                        <button onclick="executeStructural('combine')" class="p-2 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 rounded text-xs font-semibold transition cursor-pointer">🧲 尝试合并同类项</button>
                        <button onclick="executeStructural('bracket')" class="p-2 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 rounded text-xs font-semibold transition cursor-pointer">🫧 尝试解开力场括号</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col flex-1 min-h-[300px]">
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-mono mb-2">🧠 辩护与反思检测系统</div>
                
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 bg-slate-900/60 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl">🤖</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-indigo-400">导学向导: Equi</h4>
                        <span class="text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-indigo-950 text-indigo-300 rounded border border-indigo-800">试错与逻辑反思</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-900/40 rounded-lg p-3 border border-slate-800 overflow-y-auto mb-4 text-xs" id="ai-chat-box"></div>

                <div class="space-y-2 hidden" id="defense-zone">
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-purple-400 font-bold block uppercase tracking-wider">💡 当你解出 x 后，请在此做出逻辑辩护：</span>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2" id="defense-options"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800 p-3 text-center text-xs text-slate-500">
        Equilibrium Engine v2.0.0 © 2026 | 真实开放试错沙盒架构
    </footer>

    <script>
        // 核心课程与多维目标配置
        const levelsData = [
            { id: 1, name: "LEVEL 1: 加减逆元", validAnswers: ["x+3=8", "3+x=8"], quest: "药剂调配平衡", desc: "神秘容器中已有 3 克试剂，总重量需达到 8 克。请建立方程并亲手将其消去。", initialStructure: { lhs: { x: 1, const: 3 }, rhs: { const: 8 } }, type: 'basic', defenseQ: "你已经让未知数x孤立成功，请选择支撑你解题路径的平衡公理：", defenseA: [
                {t: "依据等式性质：在方程两边同时执行相同的加减运算，天平的平衡关系永远不会改变。", c: true},
                {t: "移项变号是纯粹的口诀，不需要理会两边同时运算的机制。", c: false}
            ]},
            { id: 2, name: "LEVEL 2: 正负整数乘除", validAnswers: ["3x=12", "3*x=12"], quest: "量子芯片克隆", desc: "3 组相同的核心纳米轨道总长为 12 微米，单组长度 x 是多少？建立方程并求解。", initialStructure: { lhs: { x: 3, const: 0 }, rhs: { const: 12 } }, type: 'muldiv', defenseQ: "当面对变量前的系数3时，为何选择对两边同时除以3？", defenseA: [
                {t: "这是为了求出单份未知数x所对应的等量份额（乘除法的逆运算关系）。", c: true},
                {t: "两边同时减去 3，就可以把变量前的系数彻底消抹掉。", c: false}
            ]},
            { id: 3, name: "LEVEL 3: 涉及「-x」项", validAnswers: ["7-x=4", "-x+7=4"], quest: "镜像反物质湮灭", desc: "正能量晶体 7 个与反物质未知箱 -x 组合后，平衡常数为 4。建立方程并解出x。", initialStructure: { lhs: { x: -1, const: 7 }, rhs: { const: 4 } }, type: 'negative_x', defenseQ: "在解出 -x = -3 状态后，你做了什么操作使其转化为正数 x 的值？", defenseA: [
                {t: "对两边同时乘以或除以 -1，逆转整体正负 charge 维度使其符号合理化。", c: true},
                {t: "直接用橡皮擦把负号抹掉，不需要对等式右边做任何改变。", c: false}
            ]},
            { id: 4, name: "LEVEL 4: 合併同類項", validAnswers: ["3x+2x=15"], quest: "磁力电荷集结", desc: "散落着两批同性质的变量电荷（3x 与 2x），总和为 15。请建模并手动合并它们。", initialStructure: { lhs: { x_terms: [3, 2], const: 0 }, rhs: { const: 15 } }, type: 'combine', defenseQ: "为什么 3x 和 2x 可以融合成 5x？", defenseA: [
                {t: "因为它们是同类项，代数特征完全一致，可以将系数部分进行合并加总。", c: true},
                {t: "因为在方程中，只要中间带加号，任何长相不同的项都可以任意加在一起。", c: false}
            ]},
            { id: 5, name: "LEVEL 5: 撤去括號", validAnswers: ["2(x+3)=14", "2*(x+3)=14"], quest: "能量晶体解封", desc: "常数力场包裹着括号。2 倍的整体包裹物 (x + 3) 与 14 平衡，请先建模并用分配律解开它。", initialStructure: { hasBracket: true, multiplier: 2, bracketInner: { x: 1, const: 3 }, rhs: { const: 14 } }, type: 'bracket', defenseQ: "当你把 2(x + 3) 展开为 2x + 6 时，依据的是什么代数法则？", defenseA: [
                {t: "依据的是乘法分配律：外部的乘数必须与括号内的每一项分别相乘。", c: true},
                {t: "只需要跟内部的第一项相乘，后面的常数 3 可以直接原样抄下来。", c: false}
            ]},
            { id: 6, name: "LEVEL 6: 消去分母", validAnswers: ["x/4=3"], quest: "液态重力引流", desc: "未知质量被稀释在 4 层流体分母之下，平衡常数为 3。请手动消去分母。", initialStructure: { lhs: { x: 1, const: 0, denominator: 4 }, rhs: { const: 3 } }, type: 'denominator', defenseQ: "要消去分母上的4，最符合代数性质的逆运算操作是什么？", defenseA: [
                {t: "两边同时乘以 4，利用乘除法的互逆关系使分母分子对消。", c: true},
                {t: "给等式两边都加上 4，这样就可以直接把下层的 4 强行消灭掉。", c: false}
            ]},
            { id: 7, name: "LEVEL 7: 括號 + 分母", validAnswers: ["(2(x-1))/3=4", "2(x-1)/3=4"], quest: "星际船闸调度", desc: "面临分母 3 和分子上的括号。请自主选择先处理分母还是括号，自力更生进行求解。", initialStructure: { lhs: { hasBracket: true, multiplier: 2, bracketInner: { x: 1, const: -1 }, denominator: 3 }, rhs: { const: 4 } }, type: 'complex_7', defenseQ: "回顾本关，你发现解多层复合方程时存在什么样的策略灵活性？", defenseA: [
                {t: "解题路径是开放多样的，既可以先消去分母，也可以先展开括号，两边的平衡永远可靠。", c: true},
                {t: "数学只有唯一的死板步骤，如果乱换顺序，天平就会彻底破裂坍塌。", c: false}
            ]},
            { id: 8, name: "LEVEL 8: 终极架构大师", validAnswers: ["(3(x+2))/4-2=4", "3(x+2)/4-2=4"], quest: "时空遗迹修补", desc: "包含了括号、分母以及独立常数项。没有任何现成步骤，依靠你前面积累的经验解出x！", initialStructure: { lhs: { hasBracket: true, multiplier: 3, bracketInner: { x: 1, const: 2 }, denominator: 4, extraConst: -2 }, rhs: { const: 4 } }, type: 'master_8', defenseQ: "恭喜！你独立战胜了最难的混合方程。请总结维持天平平衡的终极法门：", defenseA: [
                {t: "每一次代数重组或两边对等操作，虽然会让物块形态改变，但由于是对等执行，所以天平始终保持绝对平衡。", c: true},
                {t: "只要能用计算器蒙对最后的数值，中途不管做错什么都不算数。", c: false}
            ]}
        ];

        // 核心动态方程沙盒状态机结构
        let currentLevel = null;
        let activeStep = 0;      // 0: 建模, 1: 运算互动, 2: 推理辩护
        let selectedNode = null; // 当前点选的代数项特征

        // 运行时沙盒中方程的真实快照值（随着学生的任意恶搞运算而真实更新）
        let sandboxState = {
            lhs: { x_coeff: 1, const_val: 0, uncombined_x: [], hasBracket: false, multiplier: 1, bracket_x: 0, bracket_c: 0, denominator: 1, extraConst: 0 },
            rhs: { const_val: 0 }
        };

        window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            renderLevelList();
            loadLevel(1);
        });

        function renderLevelList() {
            const container = document.getElementById('level-list');
            container.innerHTML = '';
            levelsData.forEach(lvl => {
                const btn = document.createElement('button');
                btn.className = "w-full text-left p-2.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-medium flex items-center justify-between border bg-slate-800 border-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-700 cursor-pointer transition";
                btn.id = `lvl-btn-${lvl.id}`;
                btn.onclick = () => loadLevel(lvl.id);
                btn.innerHTML = `<span>${lvl.name}</span><span class='text-[10px] opacity-60 font-mono'>沙盒解题</span>`;
                container.appendChild(btn);
            });
        }

        // 重置/加载关卡
        function loadLevel(id) {
            const rawLvl = levelsData.find(l => l.id === id);
            currentLevel = JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(rawLvl));
            activeStep = 0;
            selectedNode = null;

            document.getElementById('equation-input').value = '';
            document.getElementById('equation-input').disabled = false;
            document.getElementById('modeling-zone').className = "bg-slate-900/60 p-3 rounded-lg border border-indigo-800/60 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3";

            // 初始化解析沙盒的状态树
            initSandboxState(currentLevel.initialStructure);

            lockCoreInteractive();
            document.getElementById('quest-title').innerText = currentLevel.quest;
            document.getElementById('quest-desc').innerText = currentLevel.desc;
            document.getElementById('defense-zone').classList.add('hidden');

            triggerAiDialogue(`欢迎来到关卡：**${currentLevel.name}**。<br>请先阅读现实任务情境，并在输入框中自己录入对应的代数方程。成功将其转化为方程模型后，才可解锁下方的自由计算天平。`);
        }

        function resetCurrentLevel() {
            if(currentLevel) loadLevel(currentLevel.id);
        }

        // 初始化沙盒
        function initSandboxState(initStruct) {
            sandboxState = {
                lhs: { x_coeff: 0, const_val: 0, uncombined_x: [], hasBracket: false, multiplier: 1, bracket_x: 0, bracket_c: 0, denominator: 1, extraConst: 0 },
                rhs: { const_val: 0 }
            };

            if (initStruct.hasBracket) {
                sandboxState.lhs.hasBracket = true;
                sandboxState.lhs.multiplier = initStruct.multiplier;
                sandboxState.lhs.bracket_x = initStruct.bracketInner.x;
                sandboxState.lhs.bracket_c = initStruct.bracketInner.const;
                sandboxState.lhs.denominator = initStruct.denominator || 1;
                sandboxState.lhs.extraConst = initStruct.extraConst || 0;
            } else {
                if(initStruct.lhs.x_terms) {
                    sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x = [...initStruct.lhs.x_terms];
                } else {
                    sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff = initStruct.lhs.x || 0;
                }
                sandboxState.lhs.const_val = initStruct.lhs.const || 0;
                sandboxState.lhs.denominator = initStruct.lhs.denominator || 1;
            }
            sandboxState.rhs.const_val = initStruct.rhs.const || 0;
        }

        // Phase 0: 验证建模
        function verifyModelingFormula() {
            const userInput = document.getElementById('equation-input').value.replace(/\s+/g, '').toLowerCase();
            const isMatch = currentLevel.validAnswers.some(ans => ans.replace(/\s+/g, '').toLowerCase() === userInput);

            if (isMatch) {
                activeStep = 1;
                document.getElementById('equation-input').disabled = true;
                document.getElementById('modeling-zone').className = "bg-emerald-950/40 p-3 rounded-lg border border-emerald-500/50 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3";
                
                unlockCoreInteractive();
                refreshVisualDisplay();
                triggerAiDialogue(`✨ **方程结构搭建成功！** 真实天平力场已全权交由你掌控。<br>🚨 **请注意：系统已完全移除现成步骤指引。** 如果你发生了错误运算，天平依然会维持平衡，但方程会变得一团糟！请先在下方点击你想要进行处理或消去的特定项 (Term)。`);
            } else {
                document.getElementById('modeling-zone').className = "bg-rose-950/40 p-3 rounded-lg border border-rose-500/60 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3";
                triggerAiDialogue(`⚠️ **数学模型校验失败。** 文字里的数量对等关系尚未理清，请重新检查未知数 x 与常数的组合方式再提交。`);
            }
        }

        function lockCoreInteractive() {
            document.getElementById('core-interactive-container').classList.add('opacity-30', 'pointer-events-none');
            document.getElementById('lock-overlay').classList.remove('hidden');
            lockToolbox();
        }

        function unlockCoreInteractive() {
            document.getElementById('core-interactive-container').classList.remove('opacity-30', 'pointer-events-none');
            document.getElementById('lock-overlay').classList.add('hidden');
        }

        // 刷新渲染核心显示（天平物块结构 + 字符串化代数状态）
        function refreshVisualDisplay() {
            renderSandboxEquationString();
            renderSandboxBalanceBlocks();
            checkVictoryCondition();
        }

        // 将当前的沙盒对象数据，完全动态地还原翻译为标准代数文本节点（无现成过程）
        function renderSandboxEquationString() {
            const display = document.getElementById('algebraic-display');
            display.innerHTML = '';

            // 1. 构建左盘文本链
            let lhsContainer = document.createElement('div');
            lhsContainer.className = "flex items-center gap-1";
            
            if (sandboxState.lhs.hasBracket) {
                let bracketStr = "";
                if(sandboxState.lhs.denominator !== 1) bracketStr += " [ ";
                bracketStr += `${sandboxState.lhs.multiplier} ( `;
                
                if(sandboxState.lhs.bracket_x !== 0) {
                    bracketStr += sandboxState.lhs.bracket_x === 1 ? "x" : (sandboxState.lhs.bracket_x === -1 ? "-x" : sandboxState.lhs.bracket_x + "x");
                }
                if(sandboxState.lhs.bracket_c !== 0) {
                    bracketStr += sandboxState.lhs.bracket_c > 0 ? ` + ${sandboxState.lhs.bracket_c}` : ` - ${Math.abs(sandboxState.lhs.bracket_c)}`;
                }
                bracketStr += " ) ";
                if(sandboxState.lhs.denominator !== 1) bracketStr += ` / ${sandboxState.lhs.denominator} ]`;
                
                if(sandboxState.lhs.extraConst !== 0) {
                    bracketStr += sandboxState.lhs.extraConst > 0 ? ` + ${sandboxState.lhs.extraConst}` : ` - ${Math.abs(sandboxState.lhs.extraConst)}`;
                }
                
                createInteractiveSpan(lhsContainer, bracketStr, 'bracket_block');
            } else {
                let termsCount = 0;
                // 未合并的 x 项群（Level 4）
                if (sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x.length > 0) {
                    sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x.forEach((coeff, index) => {
                        let text = `${coeff}x`;
                        if (index > 0) text = `+ ${text}`;
                        createInteractiveSpan(lhsContainer, text, `uncombined_x_${index}`);
                        termsCount++;
                    });
                } else if (sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff !== 0) {
                    let text = sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff === 1 ? "x" : (sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff === -1 ? "-x" : sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff + "x");
                    createInteractiveSpan(lhsContainer, text, 'x_term');
                    termsCount++;
                }

                // 常数项
                if (sandboxState.lhs.const_val !== 0) {
                    let cv = sandboxState.lhs.const_val;
                    let text = cv > 0 ? (termsCount > 0 ? `+ ${cv}` : `${cv}`) : (termsCount > 0 ? `- ${Math.abs(cv)}` : `${cv}`);
                    createInteractiveSpan(lhsContainer, text, 'const_term');
                    termsCount++;
                }

                // 如果分子处理完了但依然遗留着分母流体
                if (sandboxState.lhs.denominator !== 1) {
                    createInteractiveSpan(lhsContainer, `/ ${sandboxState.lhs.denominator}`, 'denominator_term');
                }

                if (termsCount === 0) {
                    createInteractiveSpan(lhsContainer, "0", 'zero_term');
                }
            }

            display.appendChild(lhsContainer);

            // 2. 等号
            let eqSpan = document.createElement('span');
            eqSpan.className = "mx-2 text-slate-500 font-bold select-none text-2xl";
            eqSpan.innerText = "＝";
            display.appendChild(eqSpan);

            // 3. 构建右盘文本链
            let rhsContainer = document.createElement('div');
            rhsContainer.className = "flex items-center gap-1";
            createInteractiveSpan(rhsContainer, `${sandboxState.rhs.const_val}`, 'rhs_const');
            display.appendChild(rhsContainer);
        }

        function createInteractiveSpan(container, text, typeId) {
            const span = document.createElement('span');
            span.className = "px-2.5 py-1 rounded bg-slate-700/60 border border-slate-600 hover:border-indigo-400 cursor-pointer font-mono term-node unselected-term";
            span.innerText = text;
            span.onclick = (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                selectNodeMechanic(typeId, span);
            };
            container.appendChild(span);
        }

        // 点选代数项锁定特征
        function selectNodeMechanic(typeId, element) {
            if (activeStep >= 2) return;

            selectedNode = typeId;
            document.querySelectorAll('.unselected-term').forEach(el => {
                el.classList.remove('bg-indigo-600', 'border-indigo-400', 'text-white', 'ring-2', 'ring-indigo-500');
            });
            element.classList.add('bg-indigo-600', 'border-indigo-400', 'text-white', 'ring-2', 'ring-indigo-500');

            const badge = document.getElementById('selected-target-badge');
            badge.innerText = `锁定目标节点 ID: ${typeId}`;
            badge.classList.remove('hidden');

            unlockToolbox();
            document.getElementById('status-indicator').className = "w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500 animate-pulse";
            document.getElementById('operation-feedback').innerText = "目标项已锁定。请在工具箱中输入任意参数，对其进行自由同等变换。";
        }

        // 真实还原天平上的物理积木堆叠（绝对水平平衡，完全同步恶搞错误运算）
        function renderSandboxBalanceBlocks() {
            const leftPan = document.getElementById('left-pan-visual');
            const rightPan = document.getElementById('right-pan-visual');
            leftPan.innerHTML = '';
            rightPan.innerHTML = '';

            // 堆砌左盘积木
            if (sandboxState.lhs.hasBracket) {
                createBlock(leftPan, `📦 ${sandboxState.lhs.multiplier}(x${sandboxState.lhs.bracket_c >= 0 ? '+' : ''}${sandboxState.lhs.bracket_c})`, 'bg-purple-700');
                if (sandboxState.lhs.denominator !== 1) createBlock(leftPan, `💧 稀释分母: ${sandboxState.lhs.denominator}`, 'bg-cyan-900/60 text-cyan-300');
                if (sandboxState.lhs.extraConst !== 0) createBlock(leftPan, `🧱 ${sandboxState.lhs.extraConst}`, 'bg-slate-600');
            } else {
                if (sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x.length > 0) {
                    sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x.forEach(c => createBlock(leftPan, `🧪 ${c}x`, 'bg-purple-600'));
                } else if (sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff !== 0) {
                    createBlock(leftPan, `🧪 ${sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff}x`, 'bg-purple-600');
                }
                if (sandboxState.lhs.const_val !== 0) {
                    createBlock(leftPan, `🧱 ${sandboxState.lhs.const_val}`, 'bg-slate-600');
                }
                if (sandboxState.lhs.denominator !== 1) {
                    createBlock(leftPan, `💧 分母: ${sandboxState.lhs.denominator}`, 'bg-cyan-900/60 text-cyan-300');
                }
            }

            // 堆砌右盘积木
            createBlock(rightPan, `💎 ${sandboxState.rhs.const_val}`, 'bg-emerald-600');
        }

        function createBlock(pan, label, bgColor) {
            const b = document.createElement('span');
            b.className = `px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold text-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 ${bgColor}`;
            b.innerText = label;
            pan.appendChild(b);
        }

        function unlockToolbox() {
            const t = document.getElementById('toolbox');
            t.classList.remove('opacity-40', 'pointer-events-none');
        }

        function lockToolbox() {
            const t = document.getElementById('toolbox');
            t.classList.add('opacity-40', 'pointer-events-none');
            document.getElementById('selected-target-badge').classList.add('hidden');
        }

        // 8. 核心自由试错算法运算机：两边绝对同增同减，绝不强制拦截
        function executeAction(actionType) {
            const valInput = document.getElementById('operation-value').value;
            const num = parseFloat(valInput);

            if (isNaN(num)) {
                document.getElementById('operation-feedback').innerText = "⚠️ 请先在小框中键入合法的常数/系数数值参数（如: 3 或 -4）！";
                return;
            }

            // 对左右托盘进行绝对平等的真实代数运算演变
            if (actionType === 'add_sub') {
                // 两边加减某个数值
                if (sandboxState.lhs.hasBracket) {
                    sandboxState.lhs.extraConst += num;
                } else {
                    sandboxState.lhs.const_val += num;
                }
                sandboxState.rhs.const_val += num;
                document.getElementById('operation-feedback').innerText = `⚡ 两边成功同时执行了加减 [ ${num} ]。天平稳如泰山，物理平衡未被破坏。`;
            } 
            else if (actionType === 'mul_div') {
                // 两边乘除某个数。
                if (sandboxState.lhs.hasBracket) {
                    // 如果存在分母，乘法直接处理分母，否则乘以外层乘数
                    if (num > 0 && sandboxState.lhs.denominator % num === 0) {
                        sandboxState.lhs.denominator /= num;
                    } else {
                        sandboxState.lhs.multiplier *= num;
                        sandboxState.lhs.extraConst *= num;
                    }
                } else {
                    // 常规运算，如果学生对非整数项盲目除法，将允许产生浮点数/分值（完美实现允许错误演算）
                    sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff = parseFloat((sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff * num).toFixed(2));
                    sandboxState.lhs.const_val = parseFloat((sandboxState.lhs.const_val * num).toFixed(2));
                    if (sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x.length > 0) {
                        sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x = sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x.map(v => parseFloat((v * num).toFixed(2)));
                    }
                }
                sandboxState.rhs.const_val = parseFloat((sandboxState.rhs.const_val * num).toFixed(2));
                document.getElementById('operation-feedback').innerText = `⚡ 两边成功同时执行了乘除 [ ${num} ]。观察代数状态，你是否让变量更接近孤立了？`;
            }

            // 清空输入框，强迫重新选定
            document.getElementById('operation-value').value = '';
            selectedNode = null;
            lockToolbox();
            refreshVisualDisplay();
        }

        // 结构性转化操作（合并同类项 / 展开括号）
        function executeStructural(type) {
            if (type === 'combine') {
                if (sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x.length > 2 || sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x.length === 2) {
                    let totalX = sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x.reduce((a,b) => a+b, 0);
                    sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff = totalX;
                    sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x = [];
                    document.getElementById('operation-feedback').innerText = "🧲 同类未知项融合聚变成功！";
                } else {
                    document.getElementById('operation-feedback').innerText = "❌ 托盘中没有未合并的同类多重变量项，此结构变形无效。";
                }
            } 
            else if (type === 'bracket') {
                if (sandboxState.lhs.hasBracket) {
                    // 展开括号泡泡：将外部 multiplier 乘以括号里面的每一项
                    let m = sandboxState.lhs.multiplier;
                    sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff = sandboxState.lhs.bracket_x * m;
                    sandboxState.lhs.const_val = (sandboxState.lhs.bracket_c * m) + sandboxState.lhs.extraConst;
                    sandboxState.lhs.hasBracket = false;
                    document.getElementById('operation-feedback').innerText = "🫧 分配律生效，玻璃括号防御泡泡被解开并破裂！";
                } else {
                    document.getElementById('operation-feedback').innerText = "❌ 这里不存在力场括号结构，无法实施分配律剥离。";
                }
            }
            selectedNode = null;
            lockToolbox();
            refreshVisualDisplay();
        }

        // 9. 胜利终极判定机制（当方程完美被学生亲手化简至 x = 目标答案时触发）
        function checkVictoryCondition() {
            if (sandboxState.lhs.hasBracket) return;
            if (sandboxState.lhs.uncombined_x.length > 0) return;
            if (sandboxState.lhs.denominator !== 1) return;

            // 动态求得当前关卡的真值解
            let expectedAnswer = 0;
            const init = currentLevel.initialStructure;
            if (currentLevel.id === 1) expectedAnswer = 5;
            if (currentLevel.id === 2) expectedAnswer = 4;
            if (currentLevel.id === 3) expectedAnswer = 3;
            if (currentLevel.id === 4) expectedAnswer = 3;
            if (currentLevel.id === 5) expectedAnswer = 4;
            if (currentLevel.id === 6) expectedAnswer = 12;
            if (currentLevel.id === 7) expectedAnswer = 7;
            if (currentLevel.id === 8) expectedAnswer = 6;

            // 必须变量系数为 1，常数修正项为 0，且右边数值刚好等于解
            if (sandboxState.lhs.x_coeff === 1 && sandboxState.lhs.const_val === 0 && sandboxState.rhs.const_val === expectedAnswer) {
                activeStep = 2; // 锁定解题
                enterDefensePhase();
            }
        }

        // Phase 3: 进入最终推理辩护模块
        function enterDefensePhase() {
            triggerAiDialogue("做得非常漂亮！你没有依赖任何现成的解题步骤提示，完全依靠自主的等量变形和试错解出了方程。现在请为你的解题路径做出最终的**逻辑理由辩护**。");
            
            const zone = document.getElementById('defense-zone');
            const opts = document.getElementById('defense-options');
            
            zone.classList.remove('hidden');
            opts.innerHTML = '';

            currentLevel.defenseA.forEach((opt, idx) => {
                const btn = document.createElement('button');
                btn.className = "w-full text-left p-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 hover:border-indigo-500 rounded text-xs transition text-slate-300 flex items-start space-x-2 cursor-pointer";
                btn.onclick = () => checkDefenseAnswer(opt.c, btn);
                btn.innerHTML = `<span class='font-bold text-indigo-400 font-mono'>${String.fromCharCode(65+idx)}.</span><span>${opt.t}</span>`;
                opts.appendChild(btn);
            });
        }

        function checkDefenseAnswer(isCorrect, element) {
            if(isCorrect) {
                element.className = "w-full text-left p-2.5 bg-emerald-950 border border-emerald-500 rounded text-xs text-emerald-300 flex items-start space-x-2";
                triggerAiDialogue(`🎉 **全维度熟练度通关！**<br>你成功解锁了该关卡的【概念理解(CU) + 程序自主试错(PU) + 渐进推理(AR)】全面指标。请点击下一关迎接更高难度的沙盒挑战！`);
                document.getElementById('status-indicator').className = "w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500";
                document.getElementById('operation-feedback').innerText = "🎉 恭喜！当前关卡已经彻底完美征服！";
            } else {
                element.className = "w-full text-left p-2.5 bg-rose-950 border border-rose-500 rounded text-xs text-rose-300 flex items-start space-x-2";
                triggerAiDialogue(`⚠️ 辩护失败。该规则属于不严谨的死记硬背观念，无法在算术和逻辑上支撑方程的恒等变换。请重新选择合理的反思逻辑。`);
            }
        }

        function triggerAiDialogue(text) {
            document.getElementById('ai-chat-box').innerHTML = `<p class='leading-relaxed'>${text}</p>`;
        }
    </script>
